 ('217', '234', 'en_us', 'A Brief History', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Church of the Transfiguration parish was founded in 1848. The building itself dates from 1850; it was made a national landmark in 1973. The founder, the Rev. Dr. George Hendric Houghton wanted to build a church that would serve the needs of the poor and marginalized, and would welcome all regardless of race, class or background.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-31 20:27:54', '2017-09-24 22:47:01', 'f971cb62-d5db-406e-956e-86f9f8f5cff4'),
