 ('221', '239', 'en_us', 'Parish Life', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Building community is an important part of Church of the Transfiguration both spiritually and socially. Many of our parishioners gather each weekon Thursdayto participate in worship and Bible Study, while others enjoy going to a local restaurant afterSundaymass to enjoy brunch and social fellowship.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-31 20:36:16', '2017-09-16 23:19:26', 'c280ba7b-b46b-4106-991b-8f85d01e64ed'),
