 ('411', '455', 'en_us', 'Baptisms', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Holy Baptism<strong>i</strong>s the sacrament welcoming an infant, child, or an adult into the body of Christ! It is an outward sign of the inward grace of Gods unconditional love for us, and as baptized persons, we are initiated into the full community and responsibilities of the Church.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ahron R. Foster', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '2017-09-23 13:50:08', '2017-09-27 23:01:05', '8fb05830-2f66-4bcc-8565-c9cbc9a7ad4b'),
