 ('180', '375', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Adult Education\",\"slug\":\"adult-education\",\"postDate\":1505579103,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<h2>The Bible and Sexuality<\\/h2><p>Adult Christian education classes at Transfiguration will resume in October with a five-week series on the Bible and sexuality. Come explore what the Hebrew Bible, Apocrypha, and New Testament have to say to us today about topics such as marriage, sexual ethics, and LGBT issues.<\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"374\"],\"12\":\"<p>Our Adult Education forums cover a wide variety of spiritual topics both within the Church and elsewhere. The series hosts a number of guest speakers and facilitators and promises an hour of entertaining and informational learning and discussion.<br><\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-09-16 16:25:03', '2017-09-16 16:25:03', '5f22ecd1-527b-4f5a-8f3a-742bccc14ed1'),
 ('181', '455', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Baptisms\",\"slug\":\"baptisms\",\"postDate\":1506174608,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":\"\",\"11\":[\"420\"],\"12\":\"<p>Pulvinar faucibus a dignissim enim accumsan arcu est nunc scelerisque parturient fringilla at vel a adipiscing id dignissim scelerisque. Nascetur mi odio a sit dis consectetur cum donec est adipiscing phasellus risus amet ultrices dis interdum. Montes dictum suspendisse consectetur vestibulum volutpat ridiculus dis nullam ac blandit tellus eu nisl lorem.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-09-23 13:50:08', '2017-09-23 13:50:08', 'bdfbcc35-820b-4622-a6cb-df5858743c06'),
 ('182', '455', '10', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"10\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Baptisms\",\"slug\":\"baptisms\",\"postDate\":1506174600,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<h3>Planning Holy Baptism<\\/h3><p>From time to time people ask about the requirements for Baptism. The only requirements to begin planning for a Baptism at Transfiguration are:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>A sincere desire to become a Christian or raise your child as a Christian.<\\/li><li>A readiness to begin (or continue) active participation in the life of the \\\"Little Church Around the Corner\\\".<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>If you are sure about both of those requirements, wonderful! It will be a delight to have you with us. The first step to planning a baptism at Transfiguration is to contact the office at 212-684-6770 and speak with the Rector of the church.<\\/p><p>If you are sure about the first requirement but not clear about the second, then we invite you to worship with us at the Church of the Transfiguration on a Sunday and meet us at the coffee hour immediately following the 11:00 am service.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Feel free to introduce yourself to the clergy, attend any of our adult education classes, or investigate our new series of Sunday Eucharistic liturgies at 11:00 am. Geared more for the needs of children and young families: \\u201cshorter and brighter\\u201d with a children\\u2019s address in place of the sermon, and featuring the Girls and Cherub Choirs. In so doing, you\'ll confirm Transfiguration is the right church home for you.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>May God bless you as you contemplate Holy Baptism for yourself or your child.<\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"420\"],\"12\":\"<p>We are pleased that you are interested in Holy Baptism at the Church of the Transfiguration. You will find here an intimate, loving, and supportive family of Christians who will do all in their power to encourage you in your life in Christ.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-09-23 13:59:55', '2017-09-23 13:59:55', 'ccbdd2c1-913d-4ac7-a1a7-c90766bc3448'),
