 ('7', '126', 'en_us', '<p>How fortunate we are to have works by all three of these masters under the roof of the Little Church. I will give thanks when December 16<sup>th</sup>rolls around.</p>', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 23:20:46', '2017-09-26 23:49:21', 'ac98a5c2-7bca-4ca5-9e8b-29c9d67d081c'),
